c: 57
v: 14
t: "They would call the believers (saying), \"Were we not with you (in the life of this world)?\" The believers would reply, \"Of course, but you let yourself be tempted. You waited, (hesitated), and entertained doubts. Your hopes and expectations deceived (and lulled) you, until the decree arrived from Allah. The master deceiver, (the Shaitan), deceived you about Allah"